  <main class="container-xxl py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-4">These terms explain how FastNotes Bot works, how billing is handled, and what we expect from you as a customer.</p>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-8">
